It is a little glitchy, but once you find the correct order to enter the info it will transmit to Fit and you will start racking up the kilometres. Hint: Sign out of Fake Sync and totally close the app > Open Fit, sign in, then minimize the app > Open Fake Sync and set the time and distance > Sign in to Fake Sync > Log your walk > Log out of Fake Sync and totally close the app > Switch back to Fit and update to make sure the info was transmitted > Open a popular walking app and Profit!
